а</div><a data-v-55fac334="" data-v-29d96cbf="" data-mode="inverted" href="/tours/uzbekistan" target="_self" class="button button_secondary button_size-s season-button" role="button"><!----><!----><span data-v-55fac334="" class="button__text-container"><span data-v-55fac334="" class="button__text">Посмотреть туры</span></span></a></div></a><!----></div><div data-v-78b801db="" class="swiper-slide" style="width: 296.333px; margin-right: 8px;"><a data-v-29d96cbf="" data-v-315cb8fe="" href="https://experience.tripster.ru/experience/Istanbul/129-neobyichnyie-marshrutyi/" class="card"><img data-v-29d96cbf="" src="https://resize.tripster.ru/-wzjxLwoqJfbz0z1_14Be1HnNow=/fit-in/266x366/filters:no_upscale()/https://cdn.tripster.ru/landings-service/397e73fa9251e6d45d85dbbec20eef20.jpg" alt="Посмотреть экскурсии" fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy"><div data-v-29d96cbf="" class="card-content"><div data-v-29d96cbf="" class="title">Понять характер контрастного Стамбула</div><a data-v-55fac334="" data-v-29d96cbf="" data-mode="inverted" href="/experience/Istanbul/129-neobyichnyie-marshrutyi" target="_self" class="button button_secondary button_size-s season-button" role="button"><!----><!----><span data-v-55fac334="" class="button__text-container"><span data-v-55fac334="" class="button__text">Посмотреть экскурсии</span></span></a></div></a><!----></div><div data-v-78b801db="" class="swiper-slide" style="width: 296.333px; margin-right: 8px;"><a data-v-29d96cbf="" data-v-315cb8fe="" href="https://experience.tripster.ru/experience/Minsk/2721-gastronomicheskie/" class="card"><img data-v-29d96cbf="" src="https://resize.tripster.ru/ItmsFNcMMv9F_khX8OTmh8_NMY8=/fit-in/266x366/filters:no_upscale()/https://cdn.tripster.ru/landings-service/e7f4ec178a3b13b0fcd1915916a9d2b6.jpg" alt="Посмотреть экскурсии" fetchpriority="low" loading="lazy"><div data-v-29d96cbf="" class="card-content"><div data-v-29d96cbf="" class="title">Ну очень вкусно поесть в&nbsp;Минске</div><a data-v-55fac334="" data-v-29d